OL,6,F"The vote has shown that consultants
OL,7,Fdo not feel the current offer goes far
OL,8,Fenough to end the current dispute and
OL,9,Foffer a long-term solution to the
OL,10,Frecruitment and retention crisis for
OL,11,Fsenior doctors, Dr Vishal Sharma, BMA
OL,12,Fconsultants committee chair, said.
OL,14,FGiven how close the result is, the
OL,15,FBMA is giving the government "a chance
OL,16,Fto improve the offer."
