OL,6,F"In the coming days we will be further
OL,7,Fengaging with consultants, and seeking
OL,8,Ftalks with government to explore
OL,9,Fwhether the concerns expressed by our
OL,10,Fmembers during the referendum process
OL,11,Fcan be addressed," Dr Sharma added.
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,14,FVictoria Atkins said: "I hugely value
OL,15,Fthe work of NHS consultants and I am
OL,16,Fdisappointed that after weeks of
OL,17,Fconstructive negotiations the BMA has,
OL,18,Fby the narrowest of margins, rejected
OL,19,Fthis fair and reasonable offer."
