OL,3,CConsultants narrowly reject pay rise
OL,4,Cin latest ballot on government offer
OL,6,FConsultants in England currently have
OL,7,Fa mandate to take strike action until
OL,8,FJune.
OL,10,FIt comes two weeks after the Hospital
OL,11,FConsultants and Specialists
OL,12,FAssociation (HCSA), which represents
OL,13,Faround 2,000 consultants, rejected an
OL,14,Foffer from the government.
OL,16,FInstead, it urged the Conservative
OL,17,Fparty to reopen negotiations after a
OL,18,F58% 'no' vote to a package the union
OL,19,Fsaid would further erode investment as
OL,20,Fwell as being "uneven" across the
OL,21,Fprofession.
